[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m575[0m[34m of [0m[33m851[0m[31m ]--[0m
   Rule Id: [34mBD000600[0m
       Tag: [34mSecurity.Backdoor.LOLBAS.Windows[0m

   Pattern: [32m\s(advpack\.dll|appvlp|at|atbroker|bash|bginfo|bitsadmin|cdb|certutil|cl_invocation\.ps1|cl_mutexverifiers\.ps1|cmd|cmdkey|cmstp|comsvcs\.dll|control|csc|cscript|csi|devtoolslauncher|dfsvc|diskshadow|dnscmd|dnx|dotnet|dxcap|esentutl|eventvwr|excel|expand|extexport|extrac32|findstr|forfiles|ftp|gfxdownloadwrapper|gpscript|hh|ie4uinit|ieadvpack\.dll|ieaframe\.dll|ic|infdefaultinstall|installutil|jsc|makecab|manage-bde\.wsf|mavinject|mftrace|microsoft\.workflow\.compiler|mmc|msbuild|msconfig|msdeploy|msdt|mshta|mshtml\.dll|msc|msxsl|netsh|odbcconf|pcalua|pcwrun|pcwutl\.dll|pester\.bat|powerpnt|presentationhost|pubprn\.vbs|rcsi|reg|regasm|regedit|register-cimprovider|regsvcs|regsvr32|rpcping|rundll32|runonce|runscripthelper|sc|schtasks|scriptrunner|setupapi\.dll|shdocvw\.dll|shell32\.dll|slmgr\.vbs|sqldumper|sqlps|sqltoolsps|squirrel|syncappvpublishingserver|syncappvpublishingserver\.vbs|syssetup\.dll|te|tracker|tttracer|update|url\.dll|verclsid|vsjitdebugger|wab|winrm\.vbs|winword|wmic|wscript|wsl|wsreset|xwizard|zipfldr\.dll)\s[0m
[30;1m165 | [0m[35mOnce you have decoded or encoded all the chunks required, it is[0m
[30;1m166 | [0m[35mexpected you will call ``exr_decoding_destroy()`` which will clean up[0m
[30;1m167 | [0m[35mall the buffers associated with that instance of the decoding[0m
[30;1m168 | [0m[35mpipeline. If you will be reading an entire image at once, it is[0m
[30;1m169 | [0m[35mrecommended to initialize the decoding pipeline once Regardless of[0m
[30;1m170 | [0m[35musing the raw chunk API, or the richer decoding pipeline, both paths[0m
[30;1m171 | [0m[35mstart with a call to query information about the chunk to read, using[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m576[0m[34m of [0m[33m851[0m[31m ]--[0m
   Rule Id: [34mBD000600[0m
       Tag: [34mSecurity.Backdoor.LOLBAS.Windows[0m
  Severity: [36mModerate[0m, Confidence: [36mLow[0m
  Filename: [33m/openexr-3.3.3/website/OpenEXRCoreAPI.rst[0m
   Pattern: [32m\s(advpack\.dll|appvlp|at|atbroker|bash|bginfo|bitsadmin|cdb|certutil|cl_invocation\.ps1|cl_mutexverifiers\.ps1|cmd|cmdkey|cmstp|comsvcs\.dll|control|csc|cscript|csi|devtoolslauncher|dfsvc|diskshadow|dnscmd|dnx|dotnet|dxcap|esentutl|eventvwr|excel|expand|extexport|extrac32|findstr|forfiles|ftp|gfxdownloadwrapper|gpscript|hh|ie4uinit|ieadvpack\.dll|ieaframe\.dll|ic|infdefaultinstall|installutil|jsc|makecab|manage-bde\.wsf|mavinject|mftrace|microsoft\.workflow\.compiler|mmc|msbuild|msconfig|msdeploy|msdt|mshta|mshtml\.dll|msc|msxsl|netsh|odbcconf|pcalua|pcwrun|pcwutl\.dll|pester\.bat|powerpnt|presentationhost|pubprn\.vbs|rcsi|reg|regasm|regedit|register-cimprovider|regsvcs|regsvr32|rpcping|rundll32|runonce|runscripthelper|sc|schtasks|scriptrunner|setupapi\.dll|shdocvw\.dll|shell32\.dll|slmgr\.vbs|sqldumper|sqlps|sqltoolsps|squirrel|syncappvpublishingserver|syncappvpublishingserver\.vbs|syssetup\.dll|te|tracker|tttracer|update|url\.dll|verclsid|vsjitdebugger|wab|winrm\.vbs|winword|wmic|wscript|wsl|wsreset|xwizard|zipfldr\.dll)\s[0m
[30;1m150 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m151 | [0m[35m1. Read the data[0m
[30;1m152 | [0m[35m2. De-compress the data (if it is compressed)[0m
[30;1m153 | [0m[35m3. Optionally update allocation based on sample data read (deep only)[0m
[30;1m154 | [0m[35m4. Unpack the data (re-orient from the on-disk representation)[0m

[30;1m643 | [0m[35min any order. When a tiled file is written, the OpenEXR library may[0m
[30;1m644 | [0m[35mbuffer and sort the tiles, depending on the file's line order. If the[0m
[30;1m645 | [0m[35mtiles in a file have been sorted into a predictable sequence,[0m
[30;1m646 | [0m[35mapplication programs reading the file can avoid slow "seek" operations[0m
[30;1m647 | [0m[35mby reading the tiles sequentially, in the order as they appear in the[0m
